OL,4,CDeaf Norfolk sheepdog Peggy learns
OL,5,C'sign language'
OL,6, A sheepdog given up to the RSPCA when
OL,7, she lost her hearing and was unable to
OL,8, work on a farm, has been taught a form
OL,9, of sign language enabling her to "get
OL,10, back to the job she loved".
OL,12,FPeggy, a collie, was adopted in 2018 by
OL,13,Fa member of the charity's staff, whose
OL,14,Fhusband is a shepherd in Norfolk.
OL,16,FTogether they began the "long process"
OL,17,Fof teaching her how to herd using hand
OL,18,Fsignals rather than voice commands.
OL,20,FPeggy, 10, is now working part-time
OL,21,Fwith the couple's other two dogs.
